survey_response.review_text: I am writing  this for my mother. She underwent surgery fir cervical spine with Dr. Rakesh Dhake sir. My mom had ACDF cervical surgery. I am happy to say that she was so much better and pain free in 2 days after surgery. Her arm pain is completely gone. Many thanks to Dhake sir. Dr. Rakesh Dhake sir is a very good person and a best spine doctor in Mumbai.

Hello everyone, 
This is Nitin tonde.
I would like to share my excellent experience with Dr. Rakesh dhake.
Actually my mom had complaint about back pain so after doing all possible treatment our family doctor Dr.Khandeparkar sent us to Dr. Rakesh.
In first meeting only he explained everything to me and mom about treatment and he explained so well that my gets ready to do small surgery too.
Every time meeting with doctor is like boost up tonic.
We had great experience with him and he comes to our life like an angel 
Now it has been almost 2 moths for surgery and my mom doing well and that pain and agony which she had earlier that gets vanished now.
Thanks to Dr. Rakesh Dhake.

Dr Rakesh ** ********** ************* *** took time to explain my dad diagnosis thoroughly, his compassion and genuine concern made us all feel at ease, especially my dad who had a surgery. Dr Rakesh expertise and patience in addressing my dad’s health issue ( spine problem ) were impressive. I highly recommend him.

Dr. Rakesh did a spine implant surgery of my mother (69 yrs) at Siddhanchal hospital, Lower Parel. It went well, and after over a month now, she is feeling better in terms of her pain. The doctor's clinic is well maintained and his availability at his clinic as well as his reachability over phone call, whatsapp, etc. during any emergency is very flexible.

Dr. Rakesh Dhake operated me yesterday for my back problem. I had severe pain when moving and geting out of bed. Sir operated me yesterday in Andheri. It's less than 24 hours and I am already feeling so much better and pain free. I have already walked today with physio. *** ****** ***** *** ** *** **** ***** ******* ** ****** *** I can blindly recommend him to anyone with spine issue. What is best about him is he is so down to earth and approachable that I feel free to ask him anything. God bless him.

\"Dr. Rakesh is exceptionally friendly and helpful. He provided outstanding support from pre-hospitalization to discharge, and even assisted with the insurance documentation. Our experience with him was truly remarkable.\

My wife was suffering from TB of spine and was unable to walk due to pain. Rakesh sir explained us the problem and performed fixatiom surgery on my wife's spine. She is now good and pain is better. ***** ****** ** *** **** ***** ********

Very excellent surgeon,not only did he diagnose the problem but also provided proper treatment, guidance, and follow-up.
Thanks Rakesh Sir.

My mother was suffering from severe low back pain and sciatica. We came to Dr. Rakesh dhake sir for that and he explained us everything in detail. She underwent surgery for spine and now is much better without pain. *** ****** ***** *** ** *** **** ***** *******

I am immensely grateful to Dr. Rakesh Dhake for the exceptional care provided to my father during his spine surgery. From the initial consultation to the post-operative follow-ups, Dr. Rakesh Dhake demonstrated unparalleled expertise, professionalism, and compassion.The surgery itself was a success, and my father is now on the road to a remarkable recovery. Dr. Rakesh Dhake's skillful hands and thorough approach have made all the difference in my father's health and well-being.Not only did Dr. Rakesh Dhake provide excellent surgical care, but the entire team also ensured we were well-informed and supported throughout the process.I highly recommend Dr. Rakesh Dhake to anyone in need of spine surgery or related medical care. Thank you, Dr. Rakesh Dhake, for your outstanding work and for giving my father a new lease on life.

Thanks to sir for the timely rescue. No doubt it will take time for her to recover but the surgery went well and the symptoms have weaned off. I highly recommend Dr Rakesh for spinal treatments. Thank you Sir.
